T1  - Exploring Intuition and its Role in Managerial Decision Making
AU  - Dane, Erik
AU  - Pratt, Michael G.
Y1  - 2007/01/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2007.23463682
